description:
Have you ever wondered, if there is one God, one Bible, one Jesus, why is it that there are so many different denominations? Bible prophecy clearly reveals why there are so many
denominations, and the Book of Revelation especially points out the very reasons behind it.

Join Pastor Ted Wilson as he walks us through the growth of the Christian church throughout the centuries and Gods special movement for today. 

Pastor Wilson is sharing Revelation of Hope directly from Indianapolis, IN.
